From: eblevitt@sales.GBA.NYU.EDU (Erik Levitt)
Subject: Re: Why use shadow?
Date: 15 Aug 93 22:29:15 GMT

The advantage of shadow passwords is fairly simple .. if you can't physically
see the passwords it's awfully hard to just simply run those characters 
through a decrypter ...

There are other advantages too ... but someone with a lot more experience
could probably explain it a little better.

